item.title: IT coursework(fill out the questionnaire)
item.dc:creator: @P_I_M_P_3_D_Tut `Lewk_
item.description:
@P_I_M_P_3_D_Tut wrote:

  1. Is the price of dentistry putting you off [Y/N] No.
  2. Would you rather spend your money elsewhere other than the dentist. No, Dental care is important.
  3. When you try to book an appointment what is the time delay they ask you to wait? a couple months
  4. Have you seen this time delay increase with the years progressing? No.
  5. If the dentist were cheaper would you visit more often? No
  6. Do you think the dentists charge too much money in relation to the amount of time they make you wait? No
  7. Can you describe the three different bands of pricing for the NHS? No
